# Follow repository agent instructions

When the open workspace or attached files include `AGENTS.md`, `CLAUDE.md`, or a `.ai-rules/` directory, read and follow them as the source of truth for that project’s engineering rules.

Do not contradict committed repo guidance with generic global habits. Prefer loading those files over relying on duplicated policy text elsewhere.
